        The the value that was added most. If two or more values have the same most added count, the result is undefined. Any of those values might be returned. Use Mode.getValues() if you want to get all values that were added most often.
        Specified by:

        the the value that was added most. If two or more values have been added the same times, the result is undefined. Any of those values might be returned. Use getValues() if you want to get all values that were added most often.

      • getValues

        public List<Integer> getValues()
        Specified by:
        getValues in interface Mode<Integer>
        Returns:
        the values that were added most often if more than one value were added the same times. E.g. if the value 2 was added 6 times and the value 5 was added 6 times than 2 and 5 will be returned. While getValue() will return either 2 or 5.
